15	//! Logging infrastructure — severity-named macros with auto file/line capture.
16	//!
17	//! All application logging goes through `apcrl_*_now!`, `apcrl_*_if!`, and
18	//! comparison variants. No naked `println!`/`eprintln!` elsewhere in the codebase.
19	//!
20	//! Output is line-oriented to stdout. Format:
21	//!   `[LEVEL] [file:line] message`
22	//!
23	//! Suffix families:
24	//!   `_now`  — unconditional emission
25	//!   `_if`   — boolean conditional, returns the bool
26	//!   `_eq`, `_ne`, `_lt`, `_gt`, `_le`, `_ge` — comparison conditional,
27	//!            stringifies arguments, returns the bool
